Replace the letter a, with b. Count how many b's are in the string.
string: "abbbabbbaaaabaabaababcabababaaabaababcabababbabbbcaabababacbababababababababababa"

string = "abbbabbbaaaabaabaababcabababaaabaababcabababbabbbcaabababacbababababababababababa"
x = string.replace("a" , "b")
y = x.count("b")
print(y)

